@startuml
title Acceptance 责任域边界图（L1）

' Scope:
' - 上传受理与状态查询的责任边界
' Not in scope:
' - worker 处理、reprocess、delete 内部执行细节
' See also:
' - ./ingest-acceptance-upload-sequence.puml
' - ./ingest-acceptance-status-sequence.puml
' - ../shared/ingest-shared-state-machine.puml

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "客户端/前端" as Client

rectangle "Acceptance Domain" {
  usecase "上传受理\nPOST /documents/upload" as UC_Upload
  usecase "状态查询\nGET /documents/{id}/status" as UC_Status
}

Client --> UC_Upload
Client --> UC_Status

note right of UC_Upload
职责：受理、幂等、保存源文件
不负责处理执行
end note

note right of UC_Status
职责：返回可观测状态
end note

@enduml
